        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h2 class="text-center text-2xl md:text-4xl">Soluciones Legales</h2>
            <p class="text-sm px-4">
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Iste
                earum hic repudiandae! Quidem eaque, quod qui nemo ipsam illo
                perferendis aut sed vitae libero quia aliquid error, similique
